This paper is related to wireless communication systems, specifically Massive MIMO, which falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The proposed scheme also involves optimizing the energy efficiency of the system, which can be categorized under Control Engineering (cs.SY) and Mobile Computing (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves partitioning the cellular coverage area, which can be related to Computer Engineering (cs.CE) as it involves designing and optimizing hardware systems.
